# =============================================================================
# üîß TROUBLESHOOTING
# =============================================================================
#
# ‚ùå Problem: Override not working
# ‚úÖ Solution: Check that .env.manifest.local is in project root, not in subdirectories
#
# ‚ùå Problem: Variable not recognized
# ‚úÖ Solution: Ensure variable name starts with MANIFEST_ and matches exactly
#
# ‚ùå Problem: Still using global settings
# ‚úÖ Solution: Run 'manifest config' to see which settings are active
#
# ‚ùå Problem: File not being ignored by git
# ‚úÖ Solution: Add '.env.manifest.local' to your .gitignore file
